ta-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Hb29nbGUtUGl4ZWwtUHJvLVNtYXJ0cGhvbmUtVGVsZXBob3RvL2RwL0IwQkNRV1ZGUFc_cmVmXz1PY3RfRExhbmRpbmdTX0RfNDk1NTE0YTdfMSZ0aD0xJnRhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTExYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiOTIwMjc3ZTctNzQ3Yi00OWZkLWEyZDUtY2EwMTMyN2VhZGE4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAYUHfp5mM8aC3I3yfHADrK78rvp_as_Yut9nhgmpyhHt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoogle-Pixel-Pro-Smartphone-Telephoto%2Fdp%2FB0BCQWVFPW%3Fref_%3DOct_DLandingS_D_495514a7_1%26th%3D1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Pixel 7 Pro</a>提供 5 倍长焦和超广角镜头，具有强大的微距功能。同时，6.7 英寸 120Hz 显示屏可提供流畅的游戏性能。您还可以期待现代功能，如无线充电、强大的防水性和改进的设计。</p><p>对于许多购买者而言，最重要的是，这两款设备都提供了谷歌的无英国媒体报道软件的 Android 体验，具有首次更新和独家功能，如 Clear Calling 和免费 VPN。唯一的缺点是指纹识别器有点迟钝，而且温度在负载下会有点热。</p><p>这些也不是仅有的两种具有不错折扣的型号。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAV5zPKMC5KHkytvcvXvLYwBMyfKF1G98aHDzwW40YiU4&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdeal%2F495514a7%3FshowVariations%3Dtrue%26pf_rd_r%3D7RQPDFF3KME5HS0R3F4G%26pf_rd_t%3DEvents%26pf_rd_i%3Ddeals%26pf_rd_p%3D605d5925-0e4f-4a06-bd31-7d87dcf4a9c0%26pf_rd_s%3Dslot-14%26ref%3Ddlx_deals_gd_dcl_img_16_495514a7_dt_sl14_c0" class="rapid-with-clickid">作为更大规模销售的一部分，</a>亚马逊几乎对所有 Pixel 7 机型都进行了降价，包括不同的颜色和内存配置，有无亚马逊礼品卡。因此，如果您一直在等待交易，现在是时候采取行动了。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1